API1:
@RequestMaping("api/stock")
Get("/get_all_stock")---list of stock with all detail
Post("/create_account")----->register the user
Get("/load_amount")---->call the third party api it means the wallet or banking system api
Post("/order")--->RequestMapping(orderId)--->buying the stock
Post("/store/stockList")----->store the list of the stock
Get("status")----->order share by the user is approve or not(we can use job or schedule or call the api at fix interval of time to check the status)
Post("/update_amount")

header:implement the jwt token to authorized the user(Bearer toke)
{
 nameOfStock
 amount
 status:buying or selling
}
